1. *Svake* godine obilazimo roditelje. (We visit our parents every year.)
2. *Svake* noći sanjam iste snove. (I have the same dreams every night.)
3. *Svakog* četvrtka održavamo sastanke. (We hold meetings every Thursday.)
4. *Svako* jutro imam novi plan. (I have a new plan every morning.)
5. *Svakom* problemu prilazim sa novim rešenjem. (I approach every problem with a new solution.)